#:[mentions list_my_mentions] GET /me/mentions
#:[mentions list_my_mentions] query: limit cursor since_id unacked
#:[ack ack_mention] POST /me/mentions/{mention_id}/ack
#:[stories my_stories] GET /me/stories
#:[stories my_stories] query: role state cursor limit
#:[meta get] GET /meta
#:[project get] GET /projects/{project_id}
#:[project update] PUT /projects/{project_id}
