#:[epic_followers remove_follower] DELETE /projects/{project_id}/epics/{epic_id}/followers/{member_id}
#:[epic_owners list_owners] GET /projects/{project_id}/epics/{epic_id}/owners
#:[epic_owners add_owner] POST /projects/{project_id}/epics/{epic_id}/owners
#:[epic_owners add_owner] body: agent_id member_id
#:[epic_agents remove_agent_owner] DELETE /projects/{project_id}/epics/{epic_id}/owners/agents/{agent_id}
